content.content: 1. April 2 in each year is proclaimed as Pope John Paul II Day. 2014, c. 3, s. 1. 2. Omitted (provides for coming into force of provisions of this Act). 2014, c. 3, s. 2. 3. Omitted (enacts short title of this Act). 2014, c. 3, s. 3. ______________  Français

3. Omitted (enacts short title of this Act). 2014, c. 3, s. 3.
